{{define "files"}}
{{template "header" .}}
<section class="section-head">
  <h1>Files</h1>
  <p>aptly upload file directories입니다. Upload/delete는 multipart 처리가 필요하므로 API 콘솔 또는 curl로 수행하세요.</p>
</section>

<section class="panel">
  <ul class="list">
    {{range .Content}}
      <li>{{.}}</li>
    {{else}}
      <li class="muted">No file directories</li>
    {{end}}
  </ul>
</section>
{{template "footer" .}}
{{end}}
